data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this adorable and fully updated home-- new HVAC, new appliances, new carpet, new LVT flooring, new paint, new cabinets and vanities with quartz countertops, along with a fenced backyard and community amenities, this property is ready for you to move in and start creating lasting memories. Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom home for sale in the highly sought-after Cherokee County, boasting an excellent school district. Situated in a lovely neighborhood, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the fresh and modern updates throughout. The entire interior has been thoughtfully repainted, creating a welcoming and contemporary ambiance. The kitchen has been completely renovated with new cabinets and sleek quartz countertops. With brand new stainless steel stove, microwave, and dishwasher, culinary bliss is just a step away.  The bathrooms have also received an upgrade, featuring new vanities, stylishly designed to complement the overall decor. The addition of new toilets and faucets adds a touch of elegance and functionality. The quartz countertops continue here, enhancing the overall luxury feel.  The exterior of the house has not been forgotten, with a fresh coat of paint ensuring a striking and well-maintained curb appeal. The fenced-in backyard provides privacy and security for children.  The HVAC system is brand new, ensuring efficient and reliable temperature control throughout the seasons. Additionally, the roof and water heater are newer, providing peace of mind for years to come.  This house not only offers a comfortable and stylish living space but also provides access to fantastic community amenities. The neighborhood boasts a community pool and tennis courts, perfect for relaxation and recreational activities for the whole family to enjoy.  Cherokee County is renowned for its top-rated schools and great community. The area offers a desirable blend of convenience and tranquility, with nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment options only a short drive away.
